title: Vegas rides late birdie binge to 64, leads PGA
description: Jhonattan Vegas made five birdies on his last six holes to shoot 7-under 64 -- his best score in 45 rounds at the majors -- and leads the PGA Championship by two shots.

title: QB Williams sought to avoid Bears, book details
description: Quarterback Caleb Williams looked to find a way around the NFL's collective bargaining agreement in an effort to avoid being drafted by the Chicago Bears, details from a forthcoming book reveal.

title: McIlroy 10 behind at US PGA as Ryder Cup captains impress
description: Venezuela's Jhonattan Vegas leads the US PGA Championship with several European players close behind, but Rory McIlroy endures a tough start.

title: How Flick turned Barca's 'young musketeers' into La Liga champions
description: As Barcelona celebrate winning La Liga, Spanish football expert Guillem Balague looks at how manager Hansi Flick turned his young side into champions.

title: Best ever PL Darts night? Aspinall wins, Littler-Humphries epic and nine-darter
description: Nathan Aspinall triumphed on one of the greatest-ever Premier League nights in Aberdeen to leave Michael van Gerwen's hopes of reaching the Play-Offs hanging by a thread.

title: Vegas charges into major lead as Donald impresses and McIlroy struggles
description: Ryder Cup captain Luke Donald rolled back the years to get within three shots of the early lead at the PGA Championship, as Rory McIlroy made an error-filled start to his bid for back-to-back major titles.

title: Golden State Warriors jersey history - No. 12 - Fred LaCour (1963)
description: During his time suiting up for the Warriors, LaCour wore only jersey No. 12 and put up 4.1 points, 1.5 rebounds and 1.2 assists per game.
